data.description: What a Gem! A lot of House on this quiet street in the heart of Bellevue. You are greeted into this super clean full of character home with a large open foyer that has freshly painted walls and stairs- living room with corner gas fireplace and and dining room with a charming decorative fireplace, both rooms are freshly painted and flow openly into each other for a great place to entertain. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and a large pantry. Door off of the kitchen to the newly expanded deck with added stairs to the completely fenced in private tree lined rear yard. HUGE Clean & dry walk out basement & separate storage room, and laundry area. 4 bedrooms with an additional upper level room that could serve as a 5th bedroom/ playroom / home office! Walk to the shops and local eateries in the quaint borough of Bellevue- Minutes to 279, & McKnight Road - HWT in 2019, replaced Furnace in 2020 , replaced AC in 2021 --Warranty!
